{"type":"text","timestamp":1780925724872,"sessionID":"ses_158903c29ffee2t6kDIK4biSQu","part":{"id":"prt_ea771ee5a001E7Md2Bk1usBLDx","messageID":"msg_ea7716c47001NQwkPTuh9YcrGh","sessionID":"ses_158903c29ffee2t6kDIK4biSQu","type":"text","text":"OpenLTM has two partially overlapping provider layers: the runtime `src/providers` abstraction and a janitor-specific batch provider abstraction. I’m checking the fresh schema and queue/rebuild pieces now so the final delta distinguishes shipped source from aspirational docs.","time":{"start":1780925722202,"end":1780925724871},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0742f1a721999b37016a26c518def88191bfbe8feb1c6d76d5","phase":"commentary"}}}}
